text: Božidar Ðorđević (born 12 April 1959) is a Yugoslav rower. He competed in the men's coxed four event at the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Yugoslav male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Yugoslavia Category:Rowers at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
